</li><li class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">100 Gäste-Kärtchen:<o:p></o:p></span></b> 
<ul style="MARGIN-TOP: 0cm" type="circle">
<li class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 72.0pt"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">48 Damen und 48 Herren aus 12 Nationen<o:p></o:p></span></b> 
</li><li class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 72.0pt"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">sowie 4 Joker: 2 Damen und Herren, die überall zu Hause sind.<o:p></o:p></span></b></li></ul>
