</BIG><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial">über den Verlag<BR><SMALL style="FONT-STYLE: italic"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Days of Wonder® entwickelt und produziert Spiele unter dem Motto „Play different.™“ („Anders spielen“). Beginnend mit der konsequenten Veröffentlichung einer sehr begrenzten Anzahl an neuen Spielen, über die kompromisslose Qualität bei der Produktion von Brettspielen, bis zum einzigartigen firmeninternen Entwicklerteam für digitale Spiele – Days of Wonder erhöht beständig das Niveau der eigenen Produkte. Das Resultat ist eine unvergleichliche Reihe an Erfolgen, darunter Zug um Zug®, das weltweit bestverkaufte Eisenbahnspiel; Small World®, das legendäre Fantasyspiel um epische Eroberungen; und Memoir ''44®, die Saga über den 2. Weltkrieg mit bisher 20 Erweiterungen.</SPAN><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Days of Wonder Brettspiele werden in 30 Ländern vertrieben. Die digitalen Versionen sind im iOS App Store erhältlich, sowie auf Steam und der Days of Wonders Webseite. </SPAN></SMALL></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><SMALL style="FONT-STYLE: italic"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Der Verlag ist weiterhin der jüngste Verlag, der jemals den weltweit begehrtesten Kritikerpreis erhielt: `das deutsche Spiel des Jahres`.<BR></SPAN></SMALL></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><SMALL style="FONT-STYLE: italic"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Bis zum heutigen Tag hat der Verlag mehr als 2,5 Millionen Brettspiele verkauft und über 25 Millionen Online-Spiele ausgerichtet.&nbsp;</SPAN></SMALL></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><BIG><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><BR>MEMOIR ''44 - <EM><FONT size=4>expansion</FONT></EM> Terrain Pack<BR>&nbsp;board game/</SPAN>Brettspiel</BIG><BR><SMALL style="FONT-STYLE: italic"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></SPAN></SMALL><SPAN style="BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,153); FONT-WEIGHT: bold">englisch</SPAN></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline"></SPAN><A href="http://de.trictrac.net/news-schmugglerfamilien-auf-weltreise.php"></A><BR></SMALL></BIG></BIG>author Richard Borg<BR><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><SPAN style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Description:</SPAN></SPAN><BR><BR><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>From the sand dunes of North Africa to the mountain passes of Northern Italy; from the Pripet Marshes of Southern Belarus to the high ground surrounding Operation Market Garden... Prior to WWII, never before in history had a conflict been fought by so many men over such vast expanses of land and so many different terrain types.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>As many of you have discovered, Memoir''44 is more than just a game, it is also a complete and expandable game system in its own right.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>With this in mind, we are pleased to bring you the Memoir''44 Terrain Pack Expansion. Filled to the brim with new terrain pieces, new elite unit badges, and additional victory medals, this expansion also includes dozens of new game elements, including rules for North African warfare, minefields, big gun markers, radar stations, supply depots, airfields and more.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Pontoon: Engineers at work!</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Train: Key target for the Partisans!</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>In order to make the North-African battles more realistic, you can use the Winter/Desert Board, sold separately. With the board, you will also find some simplified campaign rules to connect several battles into a campaign and Blitz rules to play the scenarios occurring in the early years of WWII.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>requires Memoir''44 core game to play<BR>Content</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>&nbsp;66 terrain tiles<BR>&nbsp;22 landmark tiles<BR>&nbsp;20 round markers (mines, medals...)<BR>&nbsp;16 obstacles<BR>&nbsp;28 Special Unit badges<BR>&nbsp;4 Historical scenarios<BR>&nbsp;Rules in English and French</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG><BIG>&nbsp;<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Arial Narrow''; COLOR: rgb(102,0,0)">Warnhinweis: &nbsp;<SPAN class=Apple-converted-space>&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></BIG></BIG><BR style="COLOR: rgb(102,0,0)"><BIG><BIG><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Arial Narrow''; COLOR: rgb(102,0,0)">Nicht geeignet für Kinder unter 3 Jahren. Enthält verschluckbare Kleinteile.</SPAN></BIG></BIG></P></TD></TR></TABLE>
