<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><BIG><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">&nbsp;board game/</SPAN>Brettspiel</BIG><BR><SMALL style="FONT-STYLE: italic"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Narrow; FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></SPAN></SMALL><SPAN style="BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,153); FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></SPAN></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG><BIG><SMALL><FONT></FONT><STRONG><FONT style="BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffff99" face=Arial>english</FONT></STRONG><BR></SMALL></BIG></BIG><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><SPAN style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Description:</SPAN></SPAN><BR><BR><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>Ticket to Ride is a cross-country train adventure in which players collect and play matching train cards to claim railway routes connecting cities throughout North America.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
<P><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3><BIG style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(241,255,198); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px"><BIG><SMALL><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><FONT size=3>The longer the routes, the more points they earn.</FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></FONT></SPAN></SMALL></BIG></BIG></P>
